data.description: Absolutely Stunning Victorian! Grand & bright entry w/ window seat, crown molding, woodwork scrolls & hardwood floors flowing throughout the entire house. Elegant dining room w/ original fireplace & woodwork. AMAZING gourmet kitchen w/ SS appliances, tile backsplash, quartz counters, double oven & endless cabinetry w/ large island. The KIT opens to the comfortable & spacious living room w/ access to covered back deck. Formal sitting room has floor to ceiling solid wood built-ins w/ original fireplace. Master Suite walk-in closet & fireplace w/ mantle. Oversized 3 car garage w/ multiple room flex space. Large lot w/ wrap around porch & back deck. Low Washington Co Taxes. UPDATES: Sept 2022 New roof installed w/ transferrable warranty, 2023 new storm doors installed, 2023 full bathroom remodeled w/ walk-in tiled shower, tiled floor, new sink & new toilet, 2022 Ductless mini split installed on 2nd floor, google wired cameras, google doorbell & ring indoor alarm system installed in home.
